
The set of files needed:

resources:
    -> banner/* (all files are those that contain the scrolling text specs)
static:
    -> css
    -> images
templates:
    -> about.html
    -> banner.html
    -> contact.html
    -> create.html
    -> home.html
    -> layout.html
banners.py - main script to execute
common.py  - a few common declarations used in all other scripts
webAppUtils.py - a few utility functions
